snippet.title: Desiya Thalaivar Official Trailer | Aravind Raj | J M Bashir | Isaignani Ilaiyaraaja | SSR SATHYA
snippet.description:
Get a glimpse into the life and times of the revered national leader Pasumpon Muthuramalinga Thevar in the upcoming Tamil biographical film, Desiya Thalaivar (The National Leader).

Directed by R. Aravind Raj (known for films like Oomai Vizhigal and Uzhavan Magan), this much-anticipated biopic explores Thevar's contributions as a freedom fighter, his involvement in social movements like the Temple Entry movement, and his political journey.

The film stars J.M. Bashir in the titular role, portraying the celebrated leader. The music for the film is scored by the legendary Isaignani Ilaiyaraaja.

Desiya Thalaivar promises to be a powerful and inspiring cinematic tribute to one of Tamil Nadu's most influential historical figures.

Cast & Crew:

Starring: J.M. Bashir, Bharathiraja, Radharavi (and others)

Director: R. Aravind Raj

Music: Ilaiyaraaja

Producers: SS.Satya, S. Jennifer Margaret 

Production: SSR SATHYA

Goddess Lakshmi Mata is the goddess of wealth, wisdom, prosperity, grace, generosity and charm. The worship of Laxmi and the regular chanting of the chalisa is recommended, to those wishing to free their Karma of all the past misdeeds.

One word, countless emotions ‚Äì Qubool is here to touch your soul. The much-awaited track is finally out, and it‚Äôs nothing short of magical. With heartfelt lyrics, soulful vocals, and a melody that lingers long after it ends, Qubool captures the raw essence of love, longing, and acceptance. Every beat carries depth, and every word resonates with the kind of emotion that stays with you.

Whether you're in love, healing, or simply a fan of meaningful music, 'Qubool' is a song that speaks to the heart. It's the kind of track you‚Äôll want to put on repeat.
